Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...a mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a princess or something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cecil!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The body...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapman...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A lauden neiven. In your language, a "vampire."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A vampire? I thought she was\Nsome kind of weird pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that shriveled-up corpse turned into\Na hot naked chick and attacked somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance. Did she just\Nplump up like instant ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lauden neiven possess\Nterrifying regenerative powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much damage their bodies take,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,they can absorb latena,\Nthe power humans use to live, and revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Vampires, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Their race was destroyed many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess one survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd only been more cautious,\NI would've noticed sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I let someone die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved Cecil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The more important problem\Nis that the monster's still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got an emergency warrant out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You doreany can't possibly catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My bullets and your sword\Nseemed to hurt her just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If she gets surrounded by\Na SWAT team, that'll be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,SWAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're athletic and have great aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't train at all, so they're\Na lot more reliable than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Accuracy doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is your sense of smell in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, why did you have a fire\Nextinguisher when you ran down to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... I don't know.\NIt just felt like the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean by sense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an unpleasant man,\Nbut in that sense, you're worthy of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concerned about the other "bolicemen."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lauden neiven are far too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm getting a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tilarna, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been another victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Alamo Park. She killed a truck driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got witnesses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alamo? That's outside the cordon we set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd she get so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I called you here to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she move that fast\Nafter she got an arm cut off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. They're an old race.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't know" isn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't find her,\Nmore people are going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to fix that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was opposed to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No good will come of having\Na Semanian on the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Civilized society has its own set of rules,\Nand this little girl can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's enough, Superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,People are dying while\Nyou're standing here bitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:06:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for the girl,\NCecil Epps would be dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the vampire would've gotten out\Nwithout anybody noticing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and nobody would've known\Na thing was wrong until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, we're damn lucky\Nit worked out the way it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Zimmer, what are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And Exedilica works for me, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with her,\Nyou come to me first, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a snot-nosed kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to piss himself all the time\Nwhen he was a new recruit for the LA Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you got a problem, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't let every damn thing\Nsurprise you like that, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Matoba, how would you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can assume the vampire doesn't\Nknow anything about Earth society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't do anything fancy to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A K-9 unit would be the way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The police dogs are already out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got one right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So she killed the guy while he was driving,\Nand the truck crashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible she didn't attack the witnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because she deliberately wanted them alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Her arms? She had both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She regenerated them, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She got out of the truck and looked at us,\Nbut then she ran that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like she was wearing\Na black evening dress, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it had, like, a haze around it,\Nand kept shimmering... It was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like black flames burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's "Vau e Deie."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Vau e"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the basic illusion spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It can also serve as clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means she's got enough\Nof her power back to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you use this Va... Vau...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Vau e Deie. And yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You can't use it\Nwhen you're wearing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And it disappears immediately\Nif you lose concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I could tell you were by your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives a person of lowly birth like you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,--the right to look at me naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shut up.\N--the right to look at me naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to deal with the vampire.\NWhere'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The shopping mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the opposite of the way\Nthe witnesses said she went.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the police dogs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But from that building,\Nyou can overlook this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So she left the body for us to find\Nin order to see how the cops would react.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now that she's filled her belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what she wants most of all\Nis information about this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably thinks she can escape\Nfrom most people who'd try to surround her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that sarcasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you were insulting me.\NI could tell from your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a nasty guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. Anyway, we're off to the mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I want as many men\Ndown here as you can give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But make sure nobody's alone for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you find her, don't try to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can smell the vampire's latena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She went inside from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing on the security system, it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't trip the lasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she see lasers, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find something, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's close.\NI can't tell what direction, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly. Stay sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Her presence. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei! Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give him a kiss, Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It might wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex, that's sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For you or him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tony... Godnov... What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost touch with you, so we came to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And we saw you floating in the fountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tilarna?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She was taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That goddamn vampire...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get her for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell from up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I don't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're awake, young swordswoman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why have you not killed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Such strange letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How do you read them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}San-Tirysei? No, San-Teresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I see. So this is another world, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They call it "Earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So the greater gate spoken of\Nin the Book of Niba manifested?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Book of Niba?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}An old legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Such a noble scent.\NYour blood must taste delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You killed innocent people!\NThat's what a beast does!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You don't seem to understand what hunger is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If only we had time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tch. It seems we've been interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No! She's invincible right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fascinating. How many of you should I eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them out of here! She'll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see her. This'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep shooting! She's just like a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit. She got away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilarna, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's follow her. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that! Don't yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Such terrifying weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This isn't just some other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Am I in hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You'll find a grate up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Use it to escape underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell can't we find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've searched every inch of this damn mall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe she's not in the mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a subway 500 meters to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's connected to the\Nmall's ventilation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,An air duct, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's faster to go around\Nto the East Plaza Station
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and ambush her than try to go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I've been running all the time lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna make me a healthy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have to ride in those awful cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can smell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were right, huh?\NI don't know if that's good luck or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to capture that\Nvampire alive if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw how strong she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't hold back on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said "if possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did talking to her make you sympathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You take pity on her for having to run\Naround in a town she's never seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget. She's killed two people already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She almost killed Cecil, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just something I want to ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}An honor to meet you,\Ndescendant of the old blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Indeed. I apologize for being so forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What do you hope to gain by saving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tell me what it is you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Book of Niba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I thought you might know something\Nabout such an ancient book...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Were you the one who had me brought here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Not at all. I wish merely to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I need no help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Begone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But with your current strength,\Nyou'll be hard-pressed to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My, my. They take their jobs very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A little. Now, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I will have this man guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shocking... I'm disappointed,\Nbearer of the old blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I died long ago in an ancient war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is just a brief dream before the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Another body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A worker? No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so damn tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... This is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Get off! Do you want to die here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No man has ever survived\Nthree battles with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I see. Perhaps you were the warrior\Nspoken of in the prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she... dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She was smashed to pieces, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Kei,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard any thank-yous from the man
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,who should've been smashed to pieces, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you? For one thing--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a word you'll never hear me say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's call for backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I'm not saving you!\NNot a chance in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we need to start on those reports...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,People who get to rest in a coffin\Nwhen the sun comes up sure have it easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Next Time"\NNext time on {\i1}COP CRAFT{\i0}.
